snippet.title: AQUAMAN 2 (2022) Teaser Trailer - Jason Momoa, Amber Heard
snippet.description:
AQUAMAN 2 (2022) Teaser Trailer - Jason Momoa, Amber Heard

Please Subscribe my Channel

Aquaman 2: The story of a soon-to-be king of the underwater kingdom of Atlantis, Arthur Curry, who has the power to speak to animals and control water. He’s also a part of the Justice League team. Directed by James Wan, this is a popular superhero movie from the DC Universe. The superb acting of Jason Momoa and other cast members attracted many fans and the movie became one of the highest-grossing DC films ever.
Now with more than 2 years since its release, there have been talks of a sequel for the film. Fans will be excited to know that Aquaman will be back with a sequel as Warner Bros released a teaser trailer of Aquaman 2 on Youtube.

Release date

Warner Bros. has planned to release the film on December 16, 2022, as confirmed in the teaser trailer of Aquaman 2. The premiere dates of upcoming DC films are always pre-planned. So the fans will have to wait a couple of years before Aquaman 2 is released. It will be marvelous as we’ll have more action from the superhero who can control the ocean and the aquatic life in it.

￼￼

Plot

The end-credits scene of Aquaman showed how David escapes and the way he plans to travel back to the Atlantis to have revenge on Arthur. As the kingdom of Arthur is in stakes it is likely the sequel of the film will show how he uses his mighty powers to save Atlantis and his family. Since he is the new king, he will have many responsibilities. New villains can also play a crucial role like mad scientist Dr. Stephen Shin who is out to search the lost kingdom of Atlantis.

Cast

The leading cast for Aquaman 2 are as follows –
Jason Momoa plays Arthur Curry/Aquaman, Amber Heard plays Mera, Willem Dafoe plays Nuidis Vulko and Patrick Wilson plays Orm
Marius/Ocean Master.

snippet.description:
How do we define performance success? How do we give quality and effective feedback for maximum impact? In this speech, attendees will learn the power of performance feedback, how to give quality feedback, and how to utilize the data from feedback for maximum impact and performance improvement.

Stretch is a non-profit leadership and management conference that brings 500 attendees and 16 speakers from all around the world who want to build effective organizations since 2013. An international platform and community for leaders and managers to share stories, hands-on solutions and explore new trends and ideas to lead, fail, learn and stretch. snippet.title: Tallow and Marty Timelapse (Amber Haze)
snippet.description:
Marty - “Señorita Tallow. If I may ask. What do you expect to find here in Kilbrook pass? I’ve heard that it’s $10,000 for your head. If you’re looking for refuge, I’m afraid you’ve come to the wrong place, mi cariño.”

Tallow - “Lawmen sniff around here often?”

Marty - “Not lawmen… Redtowns. I suggest you keep your head down, ¿vale?”

Tallow - “I’ll take that into heart, amigo.”

Marty - “I’m flattered that you think we are friends. I cannot seem to think of anyone else I’ve been able to say that to. At least not any more…”

Tallow - “Well, friends are useful in a place like this, don’t ya think?”

Marty - “Well, Ms Tallow. There’s a difference between those who are truly your friend and those who just want to use you. Friends don’t have a ‘use’. Friends have a purpose. And that purpose is to be your friend.”

Marty and Tallow meet in person for the first time to share a nice conversation. Considering that Marty is older and wiser than Tallow, he shares his wisdom with her about living off the land and how she should handle relationships. They meet in the desert town of Kilbrook pass, which lawmen know as the town which houses the deadliest outlaws. Many lawmen refuse to investigate due to their lack of jurisdiction and gun power. Many detectives from private agencies sniff around, so outlaws in this town have to be careful about who they speak to.

snippet.title: Behind the scenes - Aquaman (2018) | Jason Momos | Amber Heard
snippet.description:
Behind the scenes - Aquaman (2018) | Jason Momos | Amber Heard

Plot -: Once home to the most advanced civilization on Earth, the city of Atlantis is now an underwater kingdom ruled by the power-hungry King Orm. With a vast army at his disposal, Orm plans to conquer the remaining oceanic people — and then the surface world. Standing in his way is Aquaman, Orm’s half-human, half-Atlantean brother and true heir to the throne. With help from royal counselor Vulko, Aquaman must retrieve the legendary Trident of Atlan and embrace his destiny as protector of the deep.

snippet.title: Amber Melanie Smith: Turn the Pain into Power. How Helping Others Heals
snippet.description: Helping others, service, activism, heroism - these things change the world, but they have a transformative effect on the self, too. In this talk, Amber will share how helping gave her a pathway to combat depression, build self-confidence, and illuminate the calling she lives for today - while showing others how to use the power of helping to heal themselves and those around them.
